        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "Crafted from polished wood, this seemingly mundane *+1 striking club* comes with a red leather strap near the handle. The mere sight of the cudgel in a guard's hand fills prisoners with dread. Good creatures are enfeebled 2 while carrying, wielding, or wearing this item crafted by the sea-witches.",
